Text	" By the end of the month , ISIL massacred 5, 000 Yazidi men ، with killings running in the hundreds in different villages .	In addition , during this latest offensive , the Islamic State advanced to within 30 km of the Iraqi Kurdish capital of اربیل in northern Iraq .	Prompted by the siege and killings of the Yazidis , on 7 اگست ، President Obama authorized targeted airstrikes in Iraq against ISIL ، along with airdrops of aid .	The UK offered the US assistance with surveillance and refuelling , and planned humanitarian airdrops to Iraqi refugees .	The US asserted that the systematic destruction of the Yazidi people by the Islamic State was genocide .
